Sentencas: In an attempt to improve the oxygen surface-exchange coefficient of yttria stabilized zirconia, we have implanted the surface with low-energy (10 keV) V and W ions.
Titulo: Surface modification of a fuel cell material by ion implantation

Sentencas: The surface concentrations of V and W under various annealing and sputtering conditions have been measured by low energy ion scattering.
Titulo: Surface modification of a fuel cell material by ion implantation

Sentencas: In addition, O-18-isotope tracer measurements have been carried out to examine the oxygen exchange behavior.
Titulo: Surface modification of a fuel cell material by ion implantation

Sentencas: For certain conditions, the oxygen uptake is enhanced.
Titulo: Surface modification of a fuel cell material by ion implantation
